  <p> I am an Assistant Professor in the <a href="https://eecs.berkeley.edu/" target="_blank">Department of Electrical Engineering and Computer Sciences</a> at the <a href="https://www.berkeley.edu/" target="_blank">University of California, Berkeley</a>. I lead the <a href="#research">Kanazawa AI Research (KAIR) lab</a> under <a href="https://bair.berkeley.edu" target="_blank">BAIR</a>. Alongside my academic work, I have served as Chief Technical Advisor for <a href="https://lumalabs.ai/" target="_blank">Luma AI</a> and on the advisory board of <a href="https://www.wonderdynamics.com/" target="_blank">Wonder Dynamics</a>. I am also an Amazon Scholar in the Frontier AI & Robotics team. <br/><br/>

